{
  "message": "conformance(dtype): expand FNP-P2C-002 fixtures to full scoped promotion matrix breadth\n\nExpand packet-002 dtype fixtures to materially reduce parity debt in the scoped\nbool/i32/i64/f32/f64 domain under the porting-to-rust workflow.\n\nDifferential corpus expansion:\n- Added missing ordered pair coverage to complete the 5x5 scoped promotion\n  cross-product in packet002 differential fixtures.\n- New differential cases include bool-bool, bool-i64/f32, i32-bool/i32/f64,\n  i64-bool/i64/f64, f32-bool/i32/i64/f32, and f64-i32/i64/f32/f64.\n\nMetamorphic corpus expansion:\n- Added additional commutativity checks across mixed integer/float and bool/float\n  pairs.\n- Added idempotence checks for bool and f64.\n- Added additional lossless-cast-destination checks for bool->f32, i32->f64,\n  and f32->f64.\n\nAdversarial corpus expansion:\n- Added malformed-token normalization cases for empty rhs, uppercase aliases,\n  whitespace-padded rhs, and numeric-literal lhs identifiers.\n- All new adversarial cases preserve fail-closed reason-code expectations\n  (`dtype_normalization_failed`).\n\nValidation for this commit candidate:\n- rch exec -- cargo test -p fnp-conformance dtype_packet002_f_suites_are_green -- --nocapture\n- rch exec -- cargo run -p fnp-conformance --bin run_test_contract_gate\n- rch exec -- cargo check --workspace --all-targets\n- rch exec -- cargo clippy --workspace --all-targets -- -D warnings\n- rch exec -- cargo fmt --check\n- UBS_MAX_DIR_SIZE_MB=0 ubs --diff\n\nAll checks passed.\n\nRefs: bd-129d",
